      • get

        public static int get(long chan_ptr,
      byte[] buf,
      long[] frame_size,
      long sec,
      int nsec,
      int options)
        Wrapper for ach_get with timeout.
        Parameters:
        chan_ptr - The channel pointer returned by ach_open
        buf - The byte array hold message data
        frame_size - On return, element 0 holds the number of bytes read from the channel
        options - OR'ed ach_get_opts values
        sec - Absolute timeout seconds
        nsec - Absolute timeout nanoseconds
        Returns:
        An integer ach_status code
